General_review: Elevation Burger is a restaurant located in Kuwait, serving a selection of Burgers, Fast Food, Healthy that delivers across Abu Ftaira, Abu Halifa, Al Masayel, Al-Bedae and Ardhiya.
Their best selling dishes are Fresh Fries, Cheese Burger, Fancy Fries and The Bello, although they have a variety of dishes and meals to choose from like Burgers, Fast Food, Healthy.
They have been reviewed 2801 times by talabat users, with a rating of 4.

General_review: Wadi Al Ghoroub is a restaurant located in Kuwait, serving a selection of Breakfast, Arabic, Falafel that delivers across Abdullah Al-Salem, Abu Ftaira, Abu Halifa, Adailiya and Al-Ahmadi.

Their best selling dishes are Super Mix Sandwich, Hummus Platter, Super Egg Sandwich and Falafel Super Sandwich, although they have a variety of dishes and meals to choose from like Breakfast, Arabic, Falafel.
They have been reviewed 31921 times by talabat users, with a rating of 4.5.

General_review: Rochas sweets is a restaurant located in Kuwait, serving a selection of Desserts, Pastries, Cakes that delivers across Abdullah Al-Mubarak - West Jeleeb, Abdullah Al-Salem, Abu Ftaira, Abu Halifa and Abu Hasaniya.
Their best selling dishes are Dolce Sweet, Snak, Fabio Sweet and The Cube, although they have a variety of dishes and meals to choose from like Desserts, Pastries, Cakes.
They have been reviewed 14290 times by talabat users, with a rating of 4.5.
